data.description: Come check out this beautifully remodeled 3 bedroom 1 1/2 bath home located right in the city of Greenville just a few blocks away from the middle and high school. Brand new siding, windows, fully remodeled kitchen and  new flooring throughout home. Laundry on main floor. Includes a spacious mud room/spare room and a three seasons porch. It also comes with a huge .5 of an acre lot that is fenced in with a barn. The barn has electric and gas ran to it with a cement floor lots of storage area above. Schedule your private tour today before this gem is gone.
